{"tid":2129798,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那原油寶投資者維權艱難 很多律師不願代理","createTime":"2020-07-29T00:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T03:14:48.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"147f7ef3b38d79e6126548c0616157e89b35c40a","tid":2129798,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:26:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/7/28/n12288788.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F7%2F28%2Fn12288788.htm&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD8Q0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=3ed71a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/7/28/n12288788.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話吸引外資入黎<br />\n<br />\n券商人士解釋說：「首先明確一個概念，投資者買到的是掛鈎特定油價合約的紙原油，並不是真正的原油合約。這種產品實質上是基於油價的收益風險進行了『再證券化<br />\n』處理的一種操作，放在券商應該被稱為收益憑證，屬於中行發行的一種有價證券，如果按照反業務實質大於形式的原則，性質上屬於證券業務。」<br />\n<br />\n有券商人士表示：原油寶這種產品顯示了大陸《證券法》的漏洞，原油寶所代表的收益憑證是否屬於證券，並沒有明確的規定。"},{"pid":"7e585b07c200660d77df491d41f5e62bac19428d","tid":2129798,"uid":156335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，叫你買券榨班百姓錢，榨完又轉個名，榨另一班，等錢洗"},{"pid":"8857d7bd15fdf661f2f5c878b0658d73da55f4c8","tid":2129798,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:29:37.000Z","msg":"去搵地方儲石油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dd69d7cb04d783f80f11117c0fcdd927b472cb","tid":2129798,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"而家隔左一排冇哂聲氣 睇死佢都唔賠"},{"pid":"a01578a18accc3bfa2766e374006c86d53efc55f","tid":2129798,"uid":119524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:33:30.000Z","msg":"但係，券商系統沒能提供負交易導致投資者構成嚴重損失，呢條數點計？"},{"pid":"6fafaedfeaa45ad0c30cb79aebe66adf28f23957","tid":2129798,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,